<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Our Gear — Open Atlas</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Field-tested gear we actually use, reviewed honestly. Affiliate disclosure included." />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#0b0d0e" />
  <link rel="icon" href="../../assets/images/meta/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,300;9..144,400;9..144,500;9..144,600&family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Fira+Code:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../assets/css/tokens.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../assets/css/base.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../assets/css/components.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../assets/css/pages.css" />
</head>
<body data-page="gear">
  <div data-site-header></div>

  <main id="main">
    <section class="hero hero--short">
      <div class="hero__media">
        <img src="../../assets/images/hero/our-gear.jpg" alt="Gear laid out on a wooden camp table at dawn." />
      </div>
      <div class="container hero__content">
        <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb">
          <ol class="breadcrumbs">
            <li><a href="../../">Home</a></li>
            <li>Our Gear</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        <span class="hero__eyebrow">Gear, tested</span>
        <h1 class="hero__title">Kit that earns its space in the rig.</h1>
        <p class="hero__sub">
          From quick day hikes to Tamolitch Falls to multi-day overland epics,
          we push our gear to the limit — and only the toughest survives.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="callout callout--info reveal" style="margin-bottom: var(--sp-5);">
          <h3 style="margin-top:0; font-size: var(--fs-lg); font-family: var(--font-ui); font-weight: 600;">Affiliate disclosure</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
            As a participant in affiliate programs — including Amazon Associates
            — we may earn a commission from qualifying purchases made through
            links on this site, at no extra cost to you. This helps support our
            overlanding trips and content creation. We only recommend gear
            we've personally tested and love.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" style="max-width: 48rem; margin-bottom: var(--sp-5);">
          <p class="lede">
            Picture this: you're scrambling up volcanic ridges at dawn, fording
            wild rivers in the FJ Cruiser, or base camping deep in national
            forests under star-packed skies. We field-test everything on real
            trips, sharing honest lessons, epic fails, and raves for the kit
            that powers our adventures.
          </p>
        </div>

        <nav aria-label="Gear categories" class="row" style="gap: var(--sp-1); margin-bottom: var(--sp-4);" data-gear-toc></nav>

        <div data-gear></div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <div data-site-footer></div>
  <script type="module" src="../../assets/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
